Game description:
                 Haunt the house: Terrortown - help a cute ghost scare as many people as you can. Go into different houses and haunt different objects. Noisy people disturbed the funny ghost in this Android game. The ghost decided to expel the people from its territory. Under cover of darkness the ghost is flying through the town, imperceptibly entering houses, hospitals, museums, and so on. It may haunt furniture, statues, and other objects and move them. Scare as many people as you can while it's still dark.

Game features:


: Colorful graphics
: Good controls
: Funny character
: Original gameplay
